data.description: Discover your dream home in this beautifully updated tri-level gem with 3 beds, 2.5 updated baths & 1,739 SF of space. Elegant formal venues, vaulted ceilings, new floors thru-out the main level & family rm, designer paint colors, & abundant architectural interest create a sense of sophistication & warmth. Stunning updated kitchen features quartz countertops, undermount sink, soft-close drawers, under-cabinet-lighting, stainless appliances, & dream center island. The inviting family room with fireplace, opens to a deck & fully fenced backyard. There’s a spacious den/office & a primary suite with a luxurious bath & walk-in closet. The 2-car garage adds convenience. Conveniently located near major highways, military base, and entertainment.
